flowcoin (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Full node daemon with Proof-of-Training consensus.
  * ResonanceNet V5 model architecture with deterministic evaluation.
  * Ed25519 signatures with Keccak-256 hashing.
  * SLIP-0010 HD key derivation.
  * Bech32m address encoding (HRP: fl).
  * Bitcoin-compatible UTXO model and script system.

 -- Haruki Tanaka <haruki@flowcoin.org>  Mon, 25 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
